commit.message:
cfg.c (dump_bb_info): Fix flags check.

2014-04-15  Teresa Johnson  <tejohnson@google.com>

	* cfg.c (dump_bb_info): Fix flags check.
	* tree-cfg.c (remove_bb): Only dump TDF_BLOCKS when removing.

2014-04-15  Teresa Johnson  <tejohnson@google.com>

	* gcc.dg/tree-prof/update-loopch.c: Update expected output.

From-SVN: r209421
